00:00:00,683 --> 00:00:05,054
This one pound bunny is the smallest rabbit in North America.
这只一磅重的小野兔是北美兔子中最小的一只

2
00:00:05,272 --> 00:00:08,858
And he lives almost exclusively in the great basin.
他几乎是生活在这个大盆地的唯一一只兔子

3
00:00:14,189 --> 00:00:17,898
If the snow were deeper, he could tunnel between bushes,
如果积雪足够深   他可以在灌木丛间穿梭

4
00:00:18,523 --> 00:00:22,690
but this winter's dusting leaves him exposed to his enemies.
但是这个冬天只是下了一层薄薄的雪   使他暴露在天敌面前

5
00:00:27,025 --> 00:00:30,596
Worst of the bunch is the long tailed weasel.
其中最厉害的要属长尾鼬

6
00:00:32,458 --> 00:00:36,305
He's no bigger than the rabbit and has bad eyesight,
他和兔子一般大   视力不好

7
00:00:37,054 --> 00:00:39,447
but his nose and ears are sharp,
但是他有着灵敏的嗅觉和听觉

8
00:00:40,996 --> 00:00:43,614
and his teeth are even sharper.
牙齿也异常锋利

